{"tid":1116541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個遇過最西嘅私補學生/家長","createTime":"2019-04-20T05:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T01:28:33.000Z","uid":232893,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc3043c7d28aa66fd2b327cb8c036401b06d76bd","tid":1116541,"uid":232893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街屌佢老母成撚日放飛機/臨時改時間<br />\n有幾次已經去到屋企門口拍門冇人打電話俾佢先知今日佢唔撚上堂<br />\n仲要佢老母都覺得完全冇問題好似覺得俾得一百幾十蚊我我就係理所當然咁要呼之則來揮之則去<br />\n平時上堂已經閪口閪面 問你攞杯水都好似蝕撚咗俾我咁<br />\n仆街私補遇到垃圾真係俾狗做"},{"pid":"61c85db37d73ca34721c9f6c8b40088566b032f4","tid":1116541,"uid":232893,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"仲有嗰啲串過馬撚嘅死𡃁仔<br />\n叫佢做乜柒都唔聽 佢老母又唔理但又唔俾你話佢鬧佢<br />\n最後溫唔曬啲嘢 又怪鳩你廢教唔到佢"},{"pid":"218d27c07a418b56b61a9bcc6c39c13e1f18864c","tid":1116541,"uid":232893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自push"},{"pid":"964e53ca908829e5faa5089b2a00c52f50e2f876","tid":1116541,"uid":90392,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"你唯一可以做嘅, 就係快啲儲多啲客, <br />\n到時係你揀客, 唔係客揀你。<br />\n<br />\n香港地, 西人佔左9成, 無計。"},{"pid":"e02abc5fc562cbeb6da5451341fee4421713f830","tid":1116541,"uid":173915,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:47:19.000Z","msg":"試過佢個仔對住我塊面放屁 佢竟然話:他只是個小孩 所以千其唔好搵大陸人家長"},{"pid":"d02154703a72bffff057ccfa9de01af9267cc3e0","tid":1116541,"uid":173915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"仲有個間屋超臭 個他隻腳更臭 成日逼我食佢煮既污糟野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s